with great confidence of his recovery.<lb/>
And within eight days space he<lb/>
grew well, and quit from his Leprosy<lb/>
divulged this Miracle, publishing with<lb/>
signal gratitude the wonders of God, and<lb/>
the praises of Gregory.<lb/>
In a Village of this <normalised orig="Kingdome" auto="true">Kingdom</normalised> (called<lb/>
<notvariant>Hihualapa</notvariant>) a Gentleman for Sixteen<lb/>
Months was tortured extremely with<lb/>
the <normalised orig="Colick" auto="true">Colic</normalised>, without being free one day<lb/>
or hour in all that time; yea, the last<lb/>
