minute. A Gentlewoman happened to<lb/>
be present, Wife to the Chief Justice of<lb/>
that Province, who told him, she had<lb/>
seen wonderful things done by the devotion<lb/>
those in her house bare to the holy<lb/>
Gregory <notvariant>Lopez</notvariant>; and, if he, with like faith,<lb/>
took him for an Intercessor to the Divine<lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <fw type="pageNum" n="84">G2</fw>
                  <pb n="25"/>
                  <lb/>
Goodness, he might be confident of<lb/>
health. The Sick Man hearing this took<lb/>
a piece of <notvariant>Gregory's</notvariant> Shirt; applying it to<lb/>
the place where his pain was sharpest,<lb/>
